&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;This role is based at the Queen Elizabeth Hospital&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Information Analyst will be responsible for the development and management of Key performance indicators, responding to ad-hoc requests and meeting the requirements of the operational performance reporting teams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;They will be responsible for producing monthly performance reports, applying complex statistical tests to the trusts performance indicators and responsible for creating automated reports that are available to the relevant stakeholders. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is essential applicants must be highly skilled in SQL andReporting Services (SSRS), excel and must be open to working with new technologies.&lt;/p&gt;
